data.description: Under contract-accepting backup offers. ***PRICE REDUCTION 10/18/2023*** Welcome home to your 2-level, 3 Bedroom/2.5 Bath attached villa in the GATED, maintenance-free community of Oak Trail! This incredible value features IMPACT WINDOWS, an attached 1 car garage, Dual Master Bedrooms with walk-in closets, upgraded laminate flooring throughout, Insulated/HURRICANE Garage Door, Vaulted Ceilings, a screened in lanai, and so much more!! The kitchen is nicely laid out and includes Stainless Steel Appliances, Corian countertops, and plenty of storage room in the closet pantry and oversized cabinets!!    This open floorplan splits your 2 downstairs bedrooms, offering both convenient access to their own full bathrooms! The 3rd bedroom is upstairs at nearly 23' x 16' - there is plenty of room to use it as you please! Game room, movie room, or just a massive 3rd bedroom, the choice is yours!     This GATED community features a playground, plenty of space to walk your dog, ample parking, and a community pool! Your ROOF maintenance is also covered by the community!!     What an ideal location! OAK TRAIL is conveniently located near I-275, just minutes from I-75, and 30-40 minutes from some of the most sought-after beaches in the country including: SIESTA KEY, ST. PETE BEACH, TREASURE ISLAND, AND ANNA MARIA ISLAND! Boating, Kayaking, Snorkeling, Hiking, Camping, Fishing, World Class Restaurants, and so much more are all nearby!! A quick 40-minute drive to Sarasota/Bradenton Airport or Tampa International Airport, and 90 minutes to Disney/Orlando! This is FLORIDA living at its absolute finest!!
